Package: DROMA.R2
Title: Grouped Meta Screening Workflow Extensions for DROMA
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-14
Authors@R:
    person("Peng Yu", "Zhong", email = "yc47680@um.edu.mo", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A workflow-oriented extension package for grouped preclinical
    biomarker screening across CellLine, PDC, PDO, and PDX datasets. The
    package reuses DROMA.Set and DROMA.R data access and clinical validation
    helpers, and adds stage-wise utilities for coverage filtering, within-study
    Wilcoxon screening, grouped meta-analysis, TCGA translation filtering, and
    workflow result assembly.
